    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Cut 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> thin slices from the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> and set them aside for serving</p><p>Finely dice the<strong> remaining tomato</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>basil</strong> coarsely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
